<h2 id=3D"id-11.SD:ForeignCurrencyAccountProductChannels-RAID-Risk,Assumpti=
ons,IssuesandDependencies">RAID - Risk, Assumptions, Issues and Dependencie=
s</h2>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p><br></p>
<h3 id=3D"id-11.SD:ForeignCurrencyAccountProductChannels-Assumptions">Assum=
ptions</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"highlight-#f4f5f7 confluenceTh" style=3D"text-align: left;vert=
ical-align: top;" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7"><p>Ref #</p></th>
<th class=3D"highlight-#f4f5f7 confluenceTh" style=3D"text-align: left;vert=
ical-align: top;" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7"><p>Assumption</p></th>
<th class=3D"highlight-#f4f5f7 confluenceTh" style=3D"text-align: left;vert=
ical-align: top;" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7"><p>Description</p></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A01</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>No Impact to Channel Systems in Phase 1 Implementation</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>The changes introduced in Phase 1 of the FCA change will not affect any =
systems or processes on the channel side. As part of the product setup with=
in the 10x platform, the required currency code is already configured and a=
vailable in both 10x and ATLAS systems. Therefore, no additional developmen=
t or integration work is needed for channel-related components during this =
phase.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A02</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Currency Code Support in 10x and ATLAS APIs</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>This existing capability ensures that currency-related data can be trans=
mitted and processed without requiring additional API enhancements or modif=
ications. As a result, integration efforts related to currency handling are=
 expected to be minimal.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A03</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Saving multi-currency beneficiary is out-of-scope</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>The current beneficiary only supports BSB / PayID so it's assumed paymen=
t to FCA or saving multi-currency beneficiary to be implemented in another =
phase.&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
