ce-resize=3D"false">4</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Remove $ symbol of the account overview, and =
not replace with correct currency symbol</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>UI change only:</strong></p><p><span =
class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"a2023c79-4d22-46b4-bea3-dde125c=
ecf4a">Based on currency code to display correct currency symbol on screen.=
</span>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Note: Channel requirement is to map correct cur=
rency symbol but not "removing" the symbol.&nbsp;</strong></p></td>
